author: Matt Walsh
description:
Today on the Matt Walsh Show, a trove of previously classified JFK files has been released. What do they say? And what does this release signify? We’ll discuss. Also, the activist judges are at it again. This time a judge has decreed that Trump is not allowed to ban trans people from the military. Have we reached a point where Trump has to go to all-out war against activist judges? Yes, we have. And Elon Musk rescues two stranded astronauts from the International Space Station. This is the kind of thing that, in earlier times, would have made him a hero. But you’ll be shocked to learn that the Left is not treating him that way.
